                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "Various Baldurians cower or stand ready to defend themselves from Mind Flayers. They grimace, awaiting the final assault... \r\n\r\n... but it does not come. The Mind Flayers no longer attack, but keep the survivors surrounded, watching and waiting.\r\n\r\nThe Baldurians look up in terror and awe as a huge shadow falls.\r\n"}
