                                    "key" : {"type" : "FixedString", "value" : "CinematicNodeContext"},
                                    "val" : {"type" : "LSString", "value" : "The Netherbrain's descent slows as it nears street level. Damaged buildings tremble, and a great cloud of dust fills the air. The watching Mind Flayers part ranks. From the dust cloud -\r\n\r\n- The Player strides forth, with Enthralled Companions. They clear a path to the Baldurians like an honour guard. A final figure drifts forward as the dust settles. The Emperor.\r\n"}
